pollock is a 2000 biographical film which tells the life story of american painter jackson pollock . it stars ed harris , marcia gay harden , jennifer connelly , robert knott , bud cort , molly regan and sada thompson , and was directed by harris . marcia gay harden won the academy award for best supporting actress for portraying lee &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , pollock 's wife . ed harris received an academy award nomination for best actor for his portrayal of pollock . the film was a long-term personal project for harris based on his previous reading of pollock 's biography .